            'Hoyle\'s carbon resonance varies ±0.5% before carbon production drops significantly — not a razor\'s edge',
            'The anthropic principle: P(observing life-permitting constants | you exist) = 1 by definition — this is not evidence of design',
            'Victor Stenger: "The universe is not fine-tuned for life. Life is fine-tuned to the universe."',
