            {'title': 'Neural Correlates of Consciousness', 'body': 'Every conscious experience — vision, emotion, decision, self-awareness — has measurable neural correlates. fMRI and EEG studies show predictable brain activity patterns preceding and accompanying all conscious states. Consciousness tracks brain activity with extraordinary fidelity.'},
