            {'myth': 'We can\'t know God\'s reasons, so the argument fails (skeptical theism)', 'reality': 'This move also destroys any ability to call God "good" in any meaningful sense — if God\'s goodness is compatible with literally any amount of observed suffering, the word "good" has been emptied of content.'},
