            {'name': 'Peter Higgs & François Englert', 'role': 'Proposed the Higgs mechanism (1964); Nobel Prize 2013 after LHC discovery'},
            {'name': 'ATLAS & CMS Collaborations', 'role': 'Discovered the Higgs boson at 125 GeV (2012) — confirming the hierarchy problem is real'},
