    {'label': 'Australopithecus', 'years_ago': 4_000_000, 'event': 'Australopithecus (including Lucy) walks upright on two legs but retains ape-like brain size. Our ancestors are unmistakably transitional.', 'category': 'evolution', 'icon': '🚶'},
